  "texts": [
    "Taking into account the possibility that earlier NEJM quizzes may have been used for training purposes, we collected the quizzes from October 2021 to March 2023.",
    "This quiz consists of images and clinical information, with readers selecting their answers from five candidate choices.",
    "While images are undoubtedly important, many questions can be answered based on clinical information alone.",
    "Two author physicians read all the quizzes and commentaries and excluded questions from the NEJM quiz that were impossible to answer without images.",
    "A third author physician was consulted when consensus could not be reached."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}